* If you need to call at least one function, your message should contain only a list of function calls and nothing else; the function calls are the response.
    {%- endraw %}
    {%- else -%} {#- force specific function -#}
You must call the following function at least one time to answer the question. You may call it multiple times if needed:
        {%- if tools_list[0].function.parameters == None or tools_list[0].function.parameters|count == 0 -%}  {#- without parameter #}
  {'name': "{{tools_list[0].function.name}}", 'description': "{{tools_list[0].function.description}}", 'arguments': null},
        {%- else -%} {#- with parameters #}
  {'name': "{{tools_list[0].function.name}}", 'description': "{{tools_list[0].function.description}}", 'arguments': { {{tools_list[0].function.parameters}} {{ '}}' }},
        {%- endif %}  {#- tools_list[0].function.parameters #}
{%- endif -%} {#- !tool_choice #}

